data.description: Here's an opportunity to say yes to the perfect address! Located in Garrett Creek's beautiful lake community on a large corner lot, this 5 bedroom 3.5 bathroom home is sure to greet you with the warmest welcome. The formal dining room, living room, and the great room (nestling custom built-in shelfing, a fireplace, & surround sound) all offer a plethora of space to gather w/ loved ones. It's uniquely designed w/ a split floorplan & tray ceilings to enhance the home's charm. The primary suite has a nook perfect for a vanity or workspace, as well as his/hers sinks & closets, jet tub w/ separate shower.  The spacious backyard creates enjoyment in any season w/ its inground pool, hot tub, & firepit! Seller bonuses include a new roof (less than one year old), as well as both the HVAC & pool serviced just for its new owners. The subdivision too has a few bonuses of its own such as lake privileges to include lakeside walkways, gazebos, benches, and docks creating easy access for fishing.
